1
00:00:19,579 --> 00:00:21,839
Greetings, Your Majesty.

2
00:00:30,699 --> 00:00:31,239
Feng,

3
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:32,560
are you cold?

4
00:00:34,359 --> 00:00:35,140
Come closer.

5
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:49,700
I've been

6
00:00:50,920 --> 00:00:52,740
thinking about you all these years.

7
00:00:55,679 --> 00:00:56,960
Thank you, Your Majesty.

8
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:59,119
But I'm here to

9
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:00,960
take Luo Yao away.

10
00:01:08,180 --> 00:01:08,819
This is

11
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:11,659
a play she and I are putting on together.

12
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:14,040
Once it's over,

13
00:01:14,519 --> 00:01:15,120
I'll

14
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:17,579
make sure she's safe.

15
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,239
Even if it's an act,

16
00:01:20,500 --> 00:01:21,680
I don't want her to suffer

17
00:01:21,799 --> 00:01:22,920
in prison.

18
00:01:24,659 --> 00:01:26,319
I must take her away today.

19
00:01:50,260 --> 00:01:51,680
Why make such a fuss?

20
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:53,900
Even if you didn't come,

21
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:56,640
that prison wouldn't hold me long.

22
00:01:58,500 --> 00:01:59,579
I know it can't hold you,

23
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,560
But I can't trap myself either.

24
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:04,439
Every moment without seeing you

25
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:07,159
is a torment.

26
00:02:11,900 --> 00:02:12,800
General Xie,

27
00:02:13,460 --> 00:02:14,340
when did you

28
00:02:15,340 --> 00:02:15,919
start saying

29
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:17,159
these sentimental words?

30
00:02:20,419 --> 00:02:20,919
Luo Yao,

31
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,080
I've never believed in gods

32
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:27,520
or fate,

33
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:29,520
but since I met you,

34
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:31,939
I've foolishly

35
00:02:33,159 --> 00:02:34,680
[I've been foolishly hoping for a future]

36
00:02:35,039 --> 00:02:35,620
[together.]

37
00:02:54,180 --> 00:02:55,620
[If we can face the storm together,]

38
00:02:56,460 --> 00:02:58,020
[our love will last forever.]

39
00:03:04,699 --> 00:03:06,219
[But I want more than just a chance.]

40
00:03:08,259 --> 00:03:10,539
[I want to be by your side]

41
00:03:14,659 --> 00:03:15,539
[until we are old.]

42
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,960
Your life is mine.

43
00:03:26,939 --> 00:03:28,460
How dare you ask for more?

44
00:03:38,860 --> 00:03:39,960
My request is simple.

45
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:43,580
Your Majesty just need to

46
00:03:44,319 --> 00:03:45,259
issue a decree to the whole country

47
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,620
that Xie Zhicang killed my brother

48
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:48,919
and all his soldiers.

49
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:49,840
Reveal the whole truth

50
00:03:50,939 --> 00:03:51,860
and clear their names.

51
00:03:52,259 --> 00:03:53,620
And give them a national funeral.

52
00:03:57,599 --> 00:04:00,159
It's not that I don't want to.

53
00:04:01,159 --> 00:04:02,219
But think about it.

54
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:03,919
If the truth comes out,

55
00:04:05,060 --> 00:04:06,159
Lingfeng's identity

56
00:04:06,819 --> 00:04:08,159
will also be made public.

57
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:09,879
How

58
00:04:11,180 --> 00:04:12,319
will he cope with it?

59
00:04:15,979 --> 00:04:17,740
He is my own flesh and blood,

60
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:20,139
and the person you care about.

61
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:23,420
How will he stand in the court

62
00:04:23,939 --> 00:04:25,040
in the future?

63
00:04:25,879 --> 00:04:26,540
What about my brother

64
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:28,040
and the 300 soldiers?

65
00:04:28,459 --> 00:04:29,540
They fought for the country,

66
00:04:29,660 --> 00:04:30,639
but died in a conspiracy,

67
00:04:30,699 --> 00:04:31,500
buried in a desolate temple.

68
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,180
Finally,

69
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:35,339
even their names became taboos.

70
00:04:36,660 --> 00:04:38,519
Your Majesty, just because you don't want to issue an edict,

71
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:39,959
do you want to let this blood debt

72
00:04:40,060 --> 00:04:41,060
pass by lightly?

73
00:04:41,819 --> 00:04:43,060
But the culprit,

74
00:04:43,139 --> 00:04:44,680
Xie Zhicang, has been punished.

75
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:53,779
Now the court is turbulent,

76
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,360
Lingfeng needs to stabilize the situation.

77
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:57,959
And he

78
00:04:58,579 --> 00:05:00,160
can also realize his ambition

79
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:01,720
to protect the world.

80
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,300
Besides, Your Majesty is still young.

81
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:07,019
Once the truth is revealed,

82
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,120
there will be another storm.

83
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:09,879
If the war comes again,

84
00:05:11,019 --> 00:05:12,579
what should the people do?

85
00:05:16,459 --> 00:05:17,860
You come from the people.

86
00:05:19,220 --> 00:05:20,839
Can you really bear to see the people

87
00:05:21,379 --> 00:05:22,279
be killed again?

88
00:05:30,779 --> 00:05:32,139
When the storm is over,

89
00:05:32,620 --> 00:05:33,519
and everything settled,

90
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:37,220
I will personally issue a decree

91
00:05:39,199 --> 00:05:41,699
to grant you a marriage with Lingfeng,

92
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,040
and confer upon you the title of Princess,

93
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,339
to have a grand wedding.

94
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:48,899
From then on,

95
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,579
you can be together

96
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,879
with a legitimate status.

97
00:05:56,100 --> 00:05:56,899
Grant a marriage?

98
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:59,079
Your Majesty, have you forgotten

99
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,259
that I'm a wanted criminal

100
00:06:02,379 --> 00:06:03,579
for killing Prince Lin'an?

101
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,000
If I have to hide my identity,

102
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:08,379
wear a mask,

103
00:06:09,220 --> 00:06:10,379
and live a precarious life

104
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:11,480
in this cruel palace,

105
00:06:13,339 --> 00:06:14,500
I'd rather not.

106
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,939
Every brick and stone

107
00:06:17,019 --> 00:06:18,079
in this palace

108
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,420
makes me sick.

109
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,199
I can't stay here any longer.

110
00:06:23,519 --> 00:06:24,279
How dare you!

111
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,100
Su Luoyao,

112
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:29,439
what do you want?

113
00:06:29,819 --> 00:06:31,319
If I wanted to kill you today,

114
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,879
no one could get close to me in this prison.

115
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,660
But I won't kill you today,

116
00:06:40,439 --> 00:06:41,980
not because I fear your power,

117
00:06:45,839 --> 00:06:47,180
but because I don't want this world

118
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,360
to be engulfed in war

119
00:06:51,759 --> 00:06:53,060
because of me.

120
00:07:00,860 --> 00:07:01,639
Xie Lingfeng.

121
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:02,680
What are you doing?

122
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,040
Put me down.

123
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:06,079
Stop it.

124
00:07:07,019 --> 00:07:08,000
Put me down.

125
00:07:12,879 --> 00:07:13,600
It's all over.

126
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:15,519
From now on,

127
00:07:15,939 --> 00:07:17,019
we will always be together.

128
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:18,959
Xie Lingfeng.

129
00:08:19,980 --> 00:08:20,879
Between you and me,

130
00:08:21,779 --> 00:08:22,819
is the deep hatred

131
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,899
owed by the Xie family.

132
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,339
From the moment we met,

133
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:27,839
we were on different paths.

134
00:08:28,980 --> 00:08:31,220
Let's part ways for this life.

135
00:08:45,639 --> 00:08:46,139
Your Majesty,

136
00:08:46,639 --> 00:08:47,759
the guards at the palace gate reported

137
00:08:48,059 --> 00:08:48,960
that last night at midnight,

138
00:08:49,259 --> 00:08:49,879
Su Luoyao

139
00:08:49,899 --> 00:08:51,480
left the imperial city alone

140
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,659
with the pass you gave her.

141
00:09:04,700 --> 00:09:06,019
I thought

142
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:09,039
if she was willing to stay for Lingfeng,

143
00:09:10,039 --> 00:09:11,679
I could spare her life.

144
00:09:13,460 --> 00:09:14,120
But

145
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:16,799
she actually left.

146
00:09:22,580 --> 00:09:24,480
Such a person who is out of control

147
00:09:25,100 --> 00:09:26,659
dares to threaten me today,

148
00:09:27,779 --> 00:09:28,379
and tomorrow,

149
00:09:29,580 --> 00:09:30,940
she will dare to turn against me.

150
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:33,799
She can't stay.

151
00:09:34,639 --> 00:09:35,360
Your Highness,

152
00:09:35,740 --> 00:09:36,299
I have already

153
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,559
followed your instructions.

154
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:39,519
That token is coated with a deadly poison

155
00:09:39,779 --> 00:09:40,779
that activates upon contact.

156
00:09:47,580 --> 00:09:48,379
I

157
00:09:49,779 --> 00:09:50,820
have been controlled by Xie Zhicang

158
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:53,559
with secrets for a lifetime.

159
00:09:58,500 --> 00:09:59,799
I will never allow

160
00:10:00,820 --> 00:10:02,539
a second threat

161
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,240
to exist in this world.

162
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:11,220
When we reach a safe place,

163
00:10:11,620 --> 00:10:12,500
I'll open a clinic

164
00:10:13,139 --> 00:10:13,720
to treat the poor

165
00:10:13,820 --> 00:10:15,340
who can't afford medical care,

166
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:16,399
for free.

167
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:19,620
With your medical skills,

168
00:10:20,139 --> 00:10:21,559
you're more likely to kill people.

169
00:10:25,980 --> 00:10:26,960
What do you want to do in the future?

170
00:10:27,940 --> 00:10:28,919
I'll find a blacksmith shop

171
00:10:29,259 --> 00:10:30,120
to forge swords,

172
00:10:30,419 --> 00:10:31,299
only selling to knights

173
00:10:31,519 --> 00:10:32,200
regardless of their status.

174
00:10:33,399 --> 00:10:33,919
My Lord,

175
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,500
what do you want to do in the future?

176
00:10:37,860 --> 00:10:38,519
I...

177
00:10:43,539 --> 00:10:44,059
My Lord!

178
00:10:44,299 --> 00:10:44,960
My Lord!

179
00:10:46,100 --> 00:10:46,559
My Lord!

180
00:10:51,299 --> 00:10:51,840
My Lord!

181
00:10:58,620 --> 00:10:59,000
Luo Yao,

182
00:10:59,200 --> 00:10:59,980
are you okay?

183
00:11:03,580 --> 00:11:04,039
Luo Yao,

184
00:11:04,159 --> 00:11:04,700
Xie Lingfeng,

185
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,600
my lady has given up

186
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,919
her revenge for you.

187
00:11:09,379 --> 00:11:10,639
How dare you come here?

188
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:12,440
What happened to Luo Yao?

189
00:11:12,539 --> 00:11:13,120
Xie Lingfeng,

190
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,720
if you have any conscience left,

191
00:11:14,860 --> 00:11:15,659
please show mercy

192
00:11:15,740 --> 00:11:16,419
and set her free,

193
00:11:17,019 --> 00:11:18,059
allowing her to

194
00:11:18,179 --> 00:11:19,220
walk her final path in peace.
